Monday to Wednesday was the window.

13
00:01:05.649 --> 00:01:07.418
- The window is shutting. Jason.
- Well. how quickly?

14
00:01:07.442 --> 00:01:09.528
Quickly.
Why didn't you tell me it was Thursday?

15
00:01:09.611 --> 00:01:11.881
It'd be weird if I kept telling you
what day of the week it was.

16
00:01:11.905 --> 00:01:14.366
- I just assume you know days.
- I'm less fertile now.

17
00:01:14.449 --> 00:01:15.802
- I can totally feel it.
- Listen. Look. Look.

18
00:01:15.826 --> 00:01:17.720
A couple of minutes
isn't gonna make a difference. is it?

19
00:01:17.744 --> 00:01:23.667
